      "type": "clever",
      "title": "Event-driven screenshot capture",
      "description": "Early on, Benjamin designed a system to capture terminal screenshots only on meaningful events (new user messages, tool results, errors) rather than polling continuously (turn 18). This avoided wasting resources and storage on redundant captures.",
      "turnIndex": 18
    },
